metadata.description: Three Panels, Million Stories. The Story of !=Avg(Joe) a.k.a. Not Average Joe is a comic strip NFT depicting how we were average Joes, made decisions to get into this space, and are growing . shilling . helping . existing today! Each panel has its own rarity trait through which you can build millions of stories. Our team and the community are waiting to hear YOUR story!
